From c1e86b4c7a992bf568f4e0004841844e8e436abd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: openigtlink-ng <ng@openigtlink.localhost>
Date: Sat, 2 May 2026 16:07:21 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] PlusOpenIGTLink: support hardened OpenIGTLink
 reimplementations via __has_include
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

PLUS's three custom igtl::* message classes (PlusClientInfoMessage,
PlusUsMessage, PlusTrackedFrameMessage) reach into protected
members of igtl::MessageBase to implement Clone() and to compute
raw-pointer offsets into the content region. That works against
the upstream OpenIGTLink C++ library, but a hardened
reimplementation may want to expose the same capability through a
sanctioned tier-2 API rather than re-exposing the raw protected
internals.

Add a single-file helper header (igtlPlusMessageCompat.h) that
self-detects which library is on the include path via
__has_include(<igtl/igtlSafeMessageHelpers.h>) and provides two
macros that PLUS's message files call:

  - IGTL_PLUS_CLONE_RECEIVED_STATE(self, src) — replaces the
    historical InitBuffer / CopyHeader / AllocateBuffer / CopyBody
    + v2 metadata-copy sequence with a single-call sanctioned API
    when the safe helpers are present, or replays the original
    sequence when they aren't.

  - IGTL_PLUS_CONTENT_BYTES(self) — returns a pointer to the start
    of the content region. Goes through the sanctioned
    GetContentPointer accessor when available; falls back to
    direct m_Content access otherwise.

Both paths produce identical observable behavior; the safe path
adds bounds checks beneath the hood. Detection is automatic via
__has_include — no build-system flags, no consumer-visible
defines.

Side-effect improvement: PlusTrackedFrameMessage::Clone() now
copies v2/v3 metadata along with header + body. Previously this
was missing — Clone() returned an instance whose metadata didn't
follow the original. Strictly additive correctness fix.
---
 .../igtlPlusClientInfoMessage.cxx             |  16 +--
 src/PlusOpenIGTLink/igtlPlusMessageCompat.h   | 124 ++++++++++++++++++
 .../igtlPlusTrackedFrameMessage.cxx           |  22 ++--
 src/PlusOpenIGTLink/igtlPlusUsMessage.cxx     |  16 +--
 4 files changed, 136 insertions(+), 42 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 src/PlusOpenIGTLink/igtlPlusMessageCompat.h

